<snippet tags="earth earthMusicA meImage" name="lifeA1">
    <div class="absoluteAlign bothHalves gameBg" style="background-image: url('assets/earth_classroom3.gif'); background-size: cover"></div>

    <img class="bwImage" src="assets/side_classroom.png" style="width: 12%; background-color: white; border: 4px double black; bottom: 38%; right: 0%" alt="drawing"/>

    <div class="absoluteAlign blackBg textPanel">
        <p>I existed around more likable, more sociable, more accomplished versions of me, who were better on every metric. Every possible reason I had to exist had already been taken by someone else.</p>

        <p>[[⮕ Next|lifeA2]]</p>
    </div>
</snippet>

<snippet tags="earth earthMusicA meImage" name="lifeA2">
    <div class="absoluteAlign bothHalves gameBg" style="background-image: url('assets/earth_classroom3.gif'); background-size: cover"></div>

    <img class="bwImage" src="assets/side_classroom.png" style="width: 12%; background-color: white; border: 4px double black; bottom: 38%; right: 0%" alt="drawing"/>

    <div class="absoluteAlign blackBg textPanel">
        <p>I was good at nothing. Even my art was unexceptional. Brian Sanborn would always be the best artist in the grade, and compared to him, my drawings were nothing. Stupid figures no one would pin to a wall.</p>

        <p>[[⮕ Next|lifeA3]]</p>
    </div>
</snippet>

<snippet tags="earth earthMusicA meImage" name="lifeA3">
    <div class="absoluteAlign bothHalves gameBg" style="background-image: url('assets/earth_classroom3.gif'); background-size: cover"></div>

    <img class="bwImage" src="assets/side_classroom.png" style="width: 12%; background-color: white; border: 4px double black; bottom: 38%; right: 0%" alt="drawing"/>

    <div class="absoluteAlign blackBg textPanel">
        <p>I couldn't picture myself happy. I didn't want a family or children or a car or a suburban home or an apartment in the city or a stable career. I couldn't imagine wanting any of those things. My future was a blank page.</p>

        <p>[[⮕ Next|lifeA4]]</p>
    </div>
</snippet>


